## ğŸ“Š Formules DAX AvancÃ©es

### Mesures de Comparaison

```dax
// Comparaison Mois PrÃ©cÃ©dent
Revenue PM = 
CALCULATE(
    [Total Revenue],
    DATEADD('data_cleaned'[Order Date], -1, MONTH)
)

Revenue vs PM % = 
DIVIDE(
    [Total Revenue] - [Revenue PM],
    [Revenue PM],
    0
) * 100

// Moyenne Mobile 3 Mois
Revenue MA3 = 
CALCULATE(
    [Total Revenue],
    DATESINPERIOD(
        'data_cleaned'[Order Date],
        LASTDATE('data_cleaned'[Order Date]),
        -3,
        MONTH
    )
) / 3
```

### Mesures de Classement

```dax
// Rang Produit
Product Rank = 
RANKX(
    ALL('data_cleaned'[Product]),
    [Total Revenue],
    ,
    DESC,
    Dense
)

// % du Total
Revenue % of Total = 
DIVIDE(
    [Total Revenue],
    CALCULATE([Total Revenue], ALL('data_cleaned')),
    0
) * 100
```

### Mesures Conditionnelles

```dax
// Indicateur de Performance
Performance Indicator = 
SWITCH(
    TRUE(),
    [YoY Growth] > 10, "ğŸŸ¢ Excellent",
    [YoY Growth] > 0, "ğŸŸ¡ Bon",
    [YoY Growth] > -5, "ğŸŸ  Attention",
    "ğŸ”´ Alerte"
)
```

